---
title: Beyond Meat® Souvlaki-Inspired Burgers with Zesty Potatoes
description: All your favourite Greek-style flavours – Beyond Meat®, Mediterranean spices,  fresh tomatoes and creamy feta mayo – are stacked between toasted buns. The result is a simple, convenient and delicious meal.

